CREATE TABLE property_inspection_records (

    inspection_date DATE,
    inspector_name VARCHAR(50),
    inspection_result VARCHAR(50)

CREATE TABLE regulation_compliance (
    compliance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    regulation_code VARCHAR(20),
    inspector_id INT,
    inspection_id INT,
    compliance_status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE property_inspection_records (
   inspection_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
   property_id INT,
   inspection_date DATE,
   inspector_name VARCHAR(50),
   inspection_result VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE property (
   property_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
   address VARCHAR(100),
   owner_name VARCHAR(50),
   property_type VARCHAR(30),
   year_built INT
);

CREATE TABLE compliance (
   compliance_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
   inspection_id INT,
   regulation_id INT,
   compliance_status VARCHAR(20),
   notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE PropertyInspections (
   inspection_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
   property_id UUID,
   inspector_name TEXT,
   inspection_date TIMESTAMP,
   compliance_status BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE Properties (
   property_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
   address TEXT,
   owner_name TEXT,
   property_type TEXT,
   inspection_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE InspectionsHistory (
   inspection_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
   property_id UUID,
   inspector_id UUID,
   inspection_date TIMESTAMP,
   compliance_status BOOLEAN
);
